A collection of miscellaneous utility classes.

          Description

Class Summary
CollectionUtils Holds several collection-related utility methods.
Notification Collects information about errors, so that multiple errors can be accounted for in a single pass instead of failing on the first error.
ObjectUtils Contains utility methods for common operations on objects.
ReflectionUtils Contains utility methods for common reflection operations.
StringUtils Some utility methods for Strings.
